The syntax for ore dictionary values is the value between double-quotes. (e.g. "ingotIron")

Examples:

The following recipe takes lava and water as inputs and creates milk (Obs: Milk isn't a real liquid, unlessyou have a mod that adds it you can't use it)
<refinery name="ExampleRecipe">
	<input1>water 1000</input1>
	<input2>lava 1000</input2>
	<output>milk 1000</output>
	<energy>120</energy>
	<delay>1</delay>
</refinery>

